<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="sl-SI">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Blockchain e-volitve 2018</title>
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.0/css/bootstrap.min.css"
          rel="stylesheet"
          integrity="sha384-9gVQ4dYFwwWSjIDZnLEWnxCjeSWFphJiwGPXr1jddIhOegiu1FwO5qRGvFXOdJZ4"
          crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="/assets/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/vue/dist/vue.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/assets/favicon.png">
</head>
<body>
<div id="app-2" class="elections-container">

    <div class="header">
        <div class="logo-wrapper">
            <a href="https://principle.network">
                <div class="logo">
                    <img src="/assets/svg/logo.svg">
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-md-center">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="cta-input">
                    <h1 class="intro-title">
                        Potrdi svojo slovensko mobilno številko
                    </h1>
                    <form  class="form" id="contact-form" @submit="submitPhone" v-if="!submitSuccess">
                        <div class="pci-input-wrapper">
                        <span class="email-icon">
                            <img src="/assets/svg/mobile.svg">
                        </span>
                            <input type="tel" class="pci-input" v-model="phone" placeholder="041 XXX XXX" required>
                            <div class="input-shadow">
                                <button class="confirm-input" type="submit">
                                    <img src="/assets/svg/send.svg">
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                    <div v-cloak>
                        <p v-if="submitError" class="notification" style="position: absolute;">{{submitError}}</p>
                        <p v-if="submitSuccess" class="notification">Hvala! V kratkem boš prejel sms s povezavo preko katere oddaš svoj glas.</p>
                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5">
                <div class="cta-text">
                    <p>Volitve so namenjene <strong>samo državljanom Republike Slovenije</strong>. Iz tega razloga preverjamo tvojo telefonsko številko.</p>

                    <p>S tem korakom boš potrdil svojo blockchain identiteto in <strong>pridobil svoj glas</strong>.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <div class="social-wrapper">
            <div class="social-icon">
                <a href="http://t.me/PrincipleNetwork">
                    <img src="/assets/svg/tg.svg">
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="social-icon">
                <a href="https://medium.com/principle">
                    <img src="/assets/svg/me.svg">
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="social-icon">
                <a href="https://twitter.com/PrincipleNet">
                    <img src="/assets/svg/tw.svg">
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="social-icon">
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/PrincipleNetwork/">
                    <img src="/assets/svg/fb.svg">
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="social-icon">
                <a href="mailto:contact@principle.network">
                    <img src="/assets/svg/em.svg">
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>
<script src="/assets/js/confirm.js"></script>
<script>
  var token = '<%- data.token %>';

  console.log('token: ', token);

  app2.token = token;
</script>
</body>
</html>